				<div>
					<p><b>DON'T LOSE ACCESS:<br />Your IP access to ForeignPolicy.com will expire on June 15</b>.</p>
					<p>To ensure uninterrupted reading, please contact Rachel Mines, sales director, at <a href="mailto:rachel.mines@foreignpolicy.com">rachel.mines@foreignpolicy.com</a>.</p>
